Revert animated view/zoom scale cache
=====================================

Date: 2026-07-02

Purpose
-------
Revert the animated scaled-view cache added in animation-scale-cache.diff.

User testing showed the repeated lag after zoom/view/fit changes is tied to the
selected scaling method, not playback state persistence. The issue does not
appear with nearest-neighbor scaling, so caching scaled animation wrappers is not
the right fix.

